Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋要裂开了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这是黑暗同盟的新一轮攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你说了不要点中份的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把品尝一半儿的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就这样开始了两个人的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我和六花  值得珍惜的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  怎么没有牵着狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}西乡隆盛，日本幕末政治家，生于鹿儿岛。其右手牵犬的塑像非常有名。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿儿岛上的西乡公像都是不带狗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊  这可是西乡公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一提到他不就应该牵着狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然搞不太清楚  我们还是去看别的西乡公像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那里竟然有狗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗在那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小组走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪儿走散的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在土产店…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}要不给他们打个电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}啊  还有这招！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么啦  好不容易考完放假了一大早就来电话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到我的留言了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区冒牌魔术师不要随便用我的语音信箱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话  快点把那些都删除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,删除？把你的存在删除吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦  我说的是那个网页
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是你擅自做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢  莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因为最近胖了就拿我来撒气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞎说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想蒙混过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  在我回来之前没删除掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着被我灌上五升牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个冒牌货  好不容易打电话给我净说些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为她会说  分别了几天想听凸守的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者问问我过得好不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说是什么网页？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里看还真是壮观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这么雄伟的火山就在我们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感应到了方圆5公里以内的共振
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近火山口处传来魔族的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是  红龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你能编出这么一大堆设定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太  莫非红龙的本体已在火山口解体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分散成了七个部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有必要把它们全都收集…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  你想到对岸去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去对岸？我们能过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  看起来可以坐船过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去对岸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Schwarz  Schnee  Scraper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑冰雪突刺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Schnee  Gretchen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒冰结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你幻想的东西应该一个都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正还有时间  不用太…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我没想到会在这里碰到勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你也是来修学旅行的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是曾经和我生死与共的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王真眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才因为太激动了才跟他抱在一起  我道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法魔王少女  苏菲娅宁·SP·萨图恩七世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你踏入了我的邪王黑暗结界的中心领域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想开战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你们俩一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人独处啊  那今天就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏菲娅宁还背负着搜寻天使的使命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我往那边  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  能不能借我500元钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会把包丢在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是天使干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且零之地带对南部地区的影响也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己回得了旅馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心  路我都记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少骗人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看出来了  其实你根本不知道怎么回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机也在包里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正世间万物都是相连的  条条大路通罗马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我肯定能回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了你  我不会再接近其他女生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你  想去哪儿就去哪儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想用钱了事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  六花？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用邪王真眼的力量很快就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着我  快点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来包里有张纸条来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:06:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}（森大人的私语）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这冒牌大人凭什么冒充森大人的名号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么  那不是你自己做的网站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守才不知道有这个网站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是你这个冒牌货做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？你觉得可能吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁干的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  是本尊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还来这里转过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里有天使的反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记不记得什么时候打开过包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友上车下车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买了零食之后分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一边吃一边在这附近转悠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  买东西的时候包还在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精之树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去有很高的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还真是在奇怪的地方意趣相投
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王真眼  有两下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭借邪王真眼之力  当然不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  是猴子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了是猴子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭借我的邪王真眼之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区一两头猿人  轻松送上西天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了  小心被咬到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想办法赶走它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话说不定会追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫  你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那之阵·改
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用这招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花退后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那之阵·改！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那之阵·改  久违地又一次成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没想到你还真记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下定决心了  永远不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是那时和勇者一同养成的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是身为魔法魔王少女所背负的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫也是个怪家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不奇怪  只是不想改变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么  游戏币吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的记忆果然已经被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太  勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  站得起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了  勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  六花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:11:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太你…已经把契约给忘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王真眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座西乡公像也不牵狗的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿儿岛上的西乡公像是不带狗的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是小鸟游同学吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她别迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话也不接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  这次全都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易你们俩单独出来玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心想要抢回包  没有顾及六花的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以七宫你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的修学旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  刚好那边有公交站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要回到车站就知道路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该减减肥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好  这里是富樫家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是七宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智音姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然打扰很抱歉  但我有些事情想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是七宫跟富樫君在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说把小鸟游同学晾在一边  他们俩玩去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小鸟游同学不是变成一个人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为我离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  富樫君做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.17,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz17.71\pos(1162,212)}收件箱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.17,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz17.71\pos(1182,336)}我是苏菲娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有地图吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到六花了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫君你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人在一起的时候还顾着七宫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她当然会生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是啊  你知道她去哪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了地图之后就跑开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  总之我来搞定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樟叶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  把你叫到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  我一个人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有人来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王真眼是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你使用任何居于最高位的光明魔法也无法战胜我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要住手的话就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我在这个世界现身的肉体反应速度极快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看破的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你就亲身体验一下魔法魔王少女的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想这么说来着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是让你来这里不是跟你战斗的  是有些事想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想着你是不是误会了我跟勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是勇者是勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直叫他勇者  勇者就是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点就让着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者跟邪王真眼缔结了恋人的契约对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到勇者就心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要跟他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样一来很多事情都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有错  魔族反应很明显
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  苏菲娅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是其他世界线的异次元现身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会渐渐失去力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉自己不再是魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这种事情已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一直这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要根据世界真理和连关天则
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为魔法魔王少女  做好我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是魔法魔王少女  苏菲娅宁·SP·萨图恩七世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃一切  与此力量一同  终我此生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以勇者的搭档是邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备一直做邪王真眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要唤醒暗炎龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把那个游戏币…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个本来就是我拿着的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是勇者好像已经不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说笑呢  这话不该我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有天使的反应了  那么我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏菲娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宫给我发了邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你在这里
