Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.48,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,596)\frz19.17\1c&H94A8B2&}邪王真眼在Water  Front  Park
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒牌货快点坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Mabinogion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个问题涉及到黑暗圣典中最复杂的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真货  肯定能答得上来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏菲娅都告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该道歉的应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于一同浴血奋战至今的漆黑烈焰使的怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让我无比悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是事实上我俩也没怎么能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说到现在才说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说都已经这时候了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说时机非常不凑巧该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不是今天就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是你生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很可能被读取思考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个情报应该属于最重要的机密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前的邮箱名上写的清清楚楚好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前那把有点破了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你收到这个会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Schwarzschild
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑伞盾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Schwarzschild
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑伞盾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前天去的地方做的  附赠的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…难道是黑暗力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备一直做邪王真眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要唤醒暗炎龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太你认为暗炎龙在你体内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会变身为GelZone  UNSAS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  暗炎龙先不说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定体内真的沉睡着什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得什么都没有才是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是觉得有什么在体内也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此  漆黑烈焰还是放不出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经放出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢你
